    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Polyurethane-106 is a complex urethane polymer that is made by a multistep process. First, Trimethyolpropane is reacted with Bis(Isocyanatomethyl)cyclohexane to form a reactive intermediate. This intermediate is then reacted with Polyhexamethylene Diisocyanate, Pentamethylene Diisocyanate, Glycerin, Sodium Hyaluronate, Maltodextrin, Tannic Acid, Cellulose Gum, and Pisum Sativum Extract"
